evvy 就可以看到激烈戰況，超好笑的，事主們醒醒啊，大家已經為台灣打起來了XDDDDD。<br />\n<br />\n#nnevvy<br />\n#我們泰國使館有小編嗎"},{"pid":"9d3e708a11ec458aa006c3a209374f4242330713","tid":1968420,"uid":38703,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5c3ded5f13a83191ecff67bd4ce7ad395dacbb16","tid":1968420,"uid":151544,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T16:01:02.000Z","msg":"有無識泰國文化既人呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T00:14:19.000Z","msg":"胡慧沖"}],"pinned":{"pid":"8bb305a8daabb3d10a8e81459a23d38c72c08c87","tid":1968420,"uid":312187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T19:11:06.000Z","msg":"打twitter戰線之如可唔可以打埋Instagram戰線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBright所屬公司都俾人開緊波<br />\n希望手足一齊入去留個言支持下佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n公司ig:gmmtv"}}